## Installation

```bash
npm install -g with-context-mcp
```

Add to your OpenCode config with your notes directory:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "with-context": {
      "command": "with-context-mcp",
      "args": ["--path", "/path/to/your/notes"]
    }
  }
}
```

For Obsidian integration, point to your vault directory.
